"```sql\nSELECT MAX(t.amount)\nFROM trans t\nJOIN account a ON t.account_id = a.account_id\nJOIN disp d ON a.account_id = d.account_id\nJOIN card c ON d.disp_id = c.disp_id\nWHERE c.issued = '1996-10-21';\n```\n\nThis SQL query finds the maximum transaction amount for a client whose card was issued on October 21, 1996. It joins the `trans`, `account`, `disp`, and `card` tables using the foreign key relationships to filter the transactions associated with the specified card issue date."